The authors of the open letter are confident that stricter legislation on civilian firearms will not prevent criminals from turning to the black market.
Now, according to him, in Moscow you can find any weapon at a low price.
Meanwhile, the Ministry of the Interior claims that the proliferation of illegal weapons is under control.
Suppliers: from factories to officials
The black market in arms is supplied through various channels.
