Subsequently, the Czech Republic exceeded, for example, the volume set for preserved mushrooms, which threatened it with a substantial fine.
The survey organizers were also interested in the idea of paying landlocked countries and the idea of granting a subsidy for applying for subsidies.
This kind of thinking did not originate in Brussels but in Prague.
"We are at a disadvantage because we have no sea.
